<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><gender1 m="他" f="她" />說希望我不要走<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽到那樣的話，<delay8 />
